title: Tainy Sledstviya
resume: Tainy Sledstviya Russian: Тайны следствия​ is a Russian television series filmed from 2000 through 2008. Since April, 2011 the new ninth season will be broadcast. The format of the series features 2 to 4, 50 minute episodes split into story arks. The television series follows the work of a female Procurator known as Maria Shvetsova. The series contains 60 episodes.
